title: Reading Screen Ivory Theme
prompt:
Title: Classic Library Home Screen
Context: Premium reading application with a classic and sophisticated aesthetic.
Description of the screen: A premium Home/Library screen for a reading app using the 'Modern Ivory' theme. The layout is elegant and spacious. At the top, a refined greeting like 'Good Evening, Reader'. Below that, a 'Currently Reading' section featuring a large, beautiful book cover with a subtle drop shadow and a minimalist progress bar. Following this is a 'My Collection' or 'Bookshelf' grid. Each book item displays a high-quality cover, title in a serif font, and author name. The UI uses thin lines, generous margins, and a palette of ivory, charcoal, and subtle gold accents for status icons. Navigation at the bottom is clean and minimalist.
Platform: ios
Form factor: phone
